    <title>Address Hotels + Resorts | LinkedIn</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Address Hotels + Resorts | 155,544 followers on LinkedIn. where life happens | Address Hotels + Resorts is a premium luxury lifestyle hotel and residence brand, located in the most sought-after locations across the region, including the UAE, Egypt, Turkey, and upcoming openings in Saudi Arabia and Bahrain. Address Hotels fusion of iconic experiences, intuitive hospitality and world-class leisure facilities are where guests come to celebrate life and its most cherished moments. 

Situated in the most sought-after locations, our hotels offer the discerning traveller ultimate access to the vibrant city life.">

