    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {"@context":"http://schema.org","@graph":[{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-03-20T14:30:10.784Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-eidalfitr-dubai-activity-7440766644483874816-sD-O","text":"Eid Al-Fitr in Dubai is marked by vibrant city experiences - from the iconic Burj Khalifa and the attractions of Downtown Dubai to waterfront walks and family-friendly entertainment across the emirate.\n\nOur latest guide highlights some of the best ways to celebrate the occasion, including city landmarks, leisure destinations, and Eid dining at Address Hotels + Resorts.\n\nRead more here: https://lnkd.in/gd779wna\n\n#AddressHotels #EidAlFitr #Dubai #LuxuryHospitality","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-eidalfitr-dubai-activity-7440766644483874816-sD-O"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-03-20T11:33:09.799Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_eidmubarak-eidalfitr-addresshotels-activity-7440722096835428352-mov6","text":"Eid Mubarak.\nWe extend our warmest wishes to our guests, partners, and colleagues celebrating Eid Al-Fitr. May this special occasion bring moments of joy, reflection, and togetherness with family and loved ones.\n\n#EidMubarak #EidAlFitr #AddressHotels #Hospitality","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_eidmubarak-eidalfitr-addresshotels-activity-7440722096835428352-mov6"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-03-05T06:00:07.957Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadan2026-umrah-activity-7435202468956950528-if5S","text":"This Holy Month, experience a seamless Umrah journey with Address Jabal Omar Makkah, thoughtfully designed for comfort and proximity to the Holy Mosque. With refined hospitality and attentive service, every detail supports a focused and peaceful pilgrimage.\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/d8MZQzuW\n\n#AddressHotels #Ramadan2026 #Umrah #JabalOmarMakkah","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadan2026-umrah-activity-7435202468956950528-if5S"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-02-24T06:00:18.385Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadan2026-iftar-activity-7431941021913157634-3p98","text":"This Ramadan, discover where to gather for the most refined Iftar experiences across Dubai with Address Hotels + Resorts.\n\nFrom elegant buffet spreads to thoughtfully curated set menus, each destination offers a setting designed for meaningful connection, exceptional dining and warm hospitality throughout the Holy Month.\n\nRead more: https://lnkd.in/dKrNfkJP\n\n#AddressHotels #Ramadan2026 #Iftar #Suhoor","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadan2026-iftar-activity-7431941021913157634-3p98"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-02-19T06:00:03.465Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_weddingsbyemaar-dubaiwedding-addresshotels-activity-7430129019968212992-obsi","text":"Celebrate your love story in the heart of Dubai with Weddings By Emaar. With iconic backdrops, luxury venues, and exceptional attention to detail, begin your forever with moments designed to last a lifetime. \n\nhttps://lnkd.in/dD92bmcZ\n\n#WeddingsByEmaar #DubaiWedding #AddressHotels #LuxuryWeddings","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_weddingsbyemaar-dubaiwedding-addresshotels-activity-7430129019968212992-obsi"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-02-17T15:17:20.839Z","headline":"","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadankareem-ramadan2026-activity-7429544490752765952-RcXD","text":"Ramadan Kareem. ✨ This Ramadan, we honour the spirit of reflection, gratitude and shared moments.\n\nMay the Holy Month bring serenity, generosity and meaningful moments of togetherness. \n\n#AddressHotels #RamadanKareem #Ramadan2026","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-ramadankareem-ramadan2026-activity-7429544490752765952-RcXD"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-02-17T09:22:12.908Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-chinesenewyear-activity-7429455118816661504-YtKD","text":"This Lunar New Year, Address Hotels + Resorts celebrates the spirit of new beginnings, honouring cherished traditions and the joy of coming together.\n\nMay the year ahead bring prosperity, good health and memorable moments shared in beautiful settings with those who matter most.\n\nHappy Chinese New Year.\n\n#AddressHotels #ChineseNewYear","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-chinesenewyear-activity-7429455118816661504-YtKD"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-01-26T14:10:51.924Z","headline":"","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-addressdowntown-burjkhalifa-activity-7421555227016806400-tUzQ","text":"Where rejuvenation meets innovation - Thank you to everyone who joined us for the Sanctum Event, celebrating the launch of The Spa Longevity at Address Downtown - against the iconic backdrop of the Burj Khalifa.\n\n#AddressHotels\n#AddressDowntown\n#BurjKhalifa","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-addressdowntown-burjkhalifa-activity-7421555227016806400-tUzQ"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-01-20T06:16:44.361Z","headline":"","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-addressbeachresortfujairah-activity-7419261582091808768-uNrR","text":"We are proud to see Address Beach Resort Fujairah showcased on the Burj Khalifa, highlighting one of the UAE’s most distinctive resort destinations.\n\nNestled into the mountains and set along the coastline, Address Beach Resort Fujairah offers a staycation escape defined by natural surroundings, refined comfort, and effortless relaxation.\n\nThis moment puts a spotlight on a destination designed for slowing down, switching off, and experiencing a different side of the UAE - where the mountains meet the sea.\n\n#AddressHotels #AddressBeachResortFujairah #BurjKhalifa #StaycationUAE #BeachsideEscape","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_addresshotels-addressbeachresortfujairah-activity-7419261582091808768-uNrR"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"DiscussionForumPosting","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts"},"datePublished":"2026-01-14T07:00:28.059Z","mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_palacedowntown-ewaan-thiptara-activity-7417098259485138944-DBsZ","text":"At Ewaan and Thiptara, dining is an expression of heritage, craftsmanship, and thoughtful hospitality.\n\nEwaan celebrates regional flavours through carefully curated menus served in refined, welcoming surroundings, offering guests an experience rooted in tradition and authenticity. Thiptara, set against the iconic Dubai Fountain, presents elegant Thai cuisine in a setting that transforms each meal into a moment to be savoured.\n\nTogether, these restaurants reflect the culinary identity of Palace Downtown - where meaningful dining experiences are shaped by quality and attention to detail.\n\n#PalaceDowntown #Ewaan #Thiptara #LuxuryDining #DowntownDubai","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/address-hotels-and-resorts_palacedowntown-ewaan-thiptara-activity-7417098259485138944-DBsZ"},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"Address Hotels + Resorts","url":"https://ae.linkedin.com/company/address-hotels-and-resorts","address":{"type":"PostalAddress","streetAddress":"Mohammed Bin Rashid Boulevard","addressLocality":"Dubai","addressRegion":"United Arab Emirates","postalCode":"n/a","addressCountry":"AE"},"description":"Address Hotels + Resorts is a premium luxury lifestyle hotel and residence brand, located in the most sought-after locations across the region, including the UAE, Egypt, Turkey, and upcoming openings in Saudi Arabia and Bahrain. Address Hotels fusion of iconic experiences, intuitive hospitality and world-class leisure facilities are where guests come to celebrate life and its most cherished moments. \n\nSituated in the most sought-after locations, our hotels offer the discerning traveller ultimate access to the vibrant city life. Downtown Dubai is the city’s busy tourism hub, home to the towering Burj Khalifa, the dancing Dubai Fountain and the sprawling Dubai Mall and The Dubai Opera. Our guests can enjoy iconic views from Dubai skylines to beach shores, along with unparallel shopping experiences at global retail, exquisite dining & wellness and easy access to business districts when they choose to stay with us.","numberOfEmployees":{"value":2309,"@type":"QuantitativeValue"},"logo":{"contentUrl":"https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4D0BAQHVLp1NyhbKfw/company-logo_200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1654694038069/address_hotels_and_resorts_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=psliK6ZjG27HSkuSzjaiIbQ6nN1k1_kfXKGzhf-dbh4","description":"Address Hotels + Resorts","@type":"ImageObject"},"slogan":"where life happens","sameAs":"http://www.addresshotels.com"}]}
    </script>
  
  
      
