<!---->
      <div class="core-section-container__content break-words">
        

          <p class="break-words text-color-text" data-test-id="about-us__description">
              Address Hotels + Resorts is a premium luxury lifestyle hotel and residence brand, located in the most sought-after locations across the region, including the UAE, Egypt, Turkey, and upcoming openings in Saudi Arabia and Bahrain. Address Hotels fusion of iconic experiences, intuitive hospitality and world-class leisure facilities are where guests come to celebrate life and its most cherished moments. 

Situated in the most sought-after locations, our hotels offer the discerning traveller ultimate access to the vibrant city life. Downtown Dubai is the city’s busy tourism hub, home to the towering Burj Khalifa, the dancing Dubai Fountain and the sprawling Dubai Mall and The Dubai Opera. Our guests can enjoy iconic views from Dubai skylines to beach shores, along with unparallel shopping experiences at global retail, exquisite dining &amp; wellness and easy access to business districts when they choose to stay with us.
          </p>

