        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">Eid Al-Fitr in Dubai is marked by vibrant city experiences - from the iconic Burj Khalifa and the attractions of Downtown Dubai to waterfront walks and family-friendly entertainment across the emirate.

