        attributed-text-segment-list__content-truncated" dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">We are proud to see Address Beach Resort Fujairah showcased on the Burj Khalifa, highlighting one of the UAE’s most distinctive resort destinations.

Nestled into the mountains and set along the coastline, Address Beach Resort Fujairah offers a staycation escape defined by natural surroundings, refined comfort, and effortless relaxation.

This moment puts a spotlight on a destination designed for slowing down, switching off, and experiencing a different side of the UAE - where the mountains meet the sea.

