  <div class="attributed-text-segment-list__container relative mt-1 mb-1.5 babybear:mt-0 babybear:mb-0.5">
    <p class="attributed-text-segment-list__content text-color-text !text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap break-words
        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">At Ewaan and Thiptara, dining is an expression of heritage, craftsmanship, and thoughtful hospitality.

Ewaan celebrates regional flavours through carefully curated menus served in refined, welcoming surroundings, offering guests an experience rooted in tradition and authenticity. Thiptara, set against the iconic Dubai Fountain, presents elegant Thai cuisine in a setting that transforms each meal into a moment to be savoured.

Together, these restaurants reflect the culinary identity of Palace Downtown - where meaningful dining experiences are shaped by quality and attention to detail.

